# VibeCraft — Epic Fantasy Knight Fighter
#
# Heroic knight with dramatic proportions and intricate details.
# 269 vertices, 400 triangles, 12 normals, 11 UVs
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.2 units tall (with raised sword ~3.4)
# Poly count  : 400 triangles
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Features:
#   - Rounded helm with golden crest and wings
#   - Ornate plate armor with pauldrons
#   - Flowing crimson cape
#   - Kite shield with heraldic design
#   - Greatsword raised in victory pose
#   - Dynamic heroic stance
#
# Material groups:
#   - armor  (polished steel)
#   - gold   (ornamental trim)
#   - cape   (deep crimson)
#   - leather (straps, grip)
#   - blade  (sword steel)
#   - shield (heraldic face)

